Package graphql.schema

Class GraphQLTypeReference

  • java.lang.Object
    • graphql.schema.GraphQLTypeReference
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GraphQLInputType, GraphQLNamedInputType, GraphQLNamedOutputType, GraphQLNamedSchemaElement, GraphQLNamedType, GraphQLOutputType, GraphQLSchemaElement, GraphQLType
    @PublicApi
public class GraphQLTypeReference
extends java.lang.Object
implements GraphQLNamedOutputType, GraphQLNamedInputType
    A special type to allow a object/interface types to reference itself. It's replaced with the real type object when the schema is built.
